ğŸ—ƒï¸ 3.2. Categorization 

Each joke was assigned to one of the following categories to help the model learn different styles of humor: 

Nasreddin Hoca â€“ traditional and moral-themed jokes 

KeloÄŸlan â€“ surreal, fairy-tale-inspired stories 

Temel â€“ regional humor from the Black Sea area 

Random â€“ modern or uncategorized jokes 

Others â€“ extremely short or unclassifiable content 

This classification enabled the model to recognize stylistic differences and generate jokes accordingly. 

