Optionally, the user can view past jokes stored on the device. 

This design strikes a balance between user-friendliness and technical efficiency. 
 Its simplicity makes the underlying GPT2-based joke generation system feel accessible, fast, and fun â€” turning artificial intelligence into an entertaining and engaging user experience. 

